## Wiring Diagram

```
  MQ-5 AO             -> GPIO 26
  BME280 SDA          -> GPIO 20
  BME280 SCL          -> GPIO 21
  GPIO 20             -> OLED SDA
  GPIO 21             -> OLED SCL
  Common GND          -> MQ-5, BME280, and OLED
  BME280 VCC          -> 3.3V
  BME280 GND          -> GND
```

